                    "image": "Sidebar_5_TreasureAndRewards.png"
                },
                "html": "The psychotropic spores of the basidirond can be harvested with a successful DC 20 <a aonid=\"8\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Herbalism Lore</a> or <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a> check, yielding 1 dose of spores (1d4 doses on a critical success); on a critical failure, the basidirond creates a 10-foot-radius hallucinogenic cloud. Each dose is worth 10 gp for use in <a aonid=\"4\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Crafting</a> poisons, or 20 gp if the poison causes the <a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">confused</a> or <a aonid=\"37\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">stupefied</a> condition."
            }
        ],
